{"title":"鞍钢工人之歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":3,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞍钢工人之歌\t一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炉膛的火焰熊熊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢流滚滚奔流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红亮的波浪翻卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里也是风起云涌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢液需要好炉温，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合格的成分有坚韧的性能，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握着样勺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧张、兴奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦急地等待喜悦的一瞬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当当当的出钢声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福洋溢心胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸笑颜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水渗入翻滚的钢水中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（炼钢工人　彭冬劲）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球磨机轰隆隆地响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿选机伴随着歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产大跃进冲天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选矿工人心花怒放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（大孤山选矿工人　杨广余）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平炉是个泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水流不完；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平炉是个宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水比金好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锹矿砂一滴汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平炉身边把钢炼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把钢钎一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼出好钢传佳音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（胡志强）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}